title: Women Holding Hands Light Skin Tone Medium Light Skin Tone
description: Represents two women with different skin tones holding hands, symbolizing friendship, love, or partnership. This emoji specifically depicts a light skin tone and a medium-dark skin tone.
apple_vendor_description: On Apple devices, the women holding hands emoji portrays a warm and inclusive gesture with two hands clasped together, featuring light and medium-light skin tones. Apple’s expert use of soft gradients and subtle shading gives the hands a natural, lifelike appearance and a gentle, rounded contour. This emoji on Apple devices powerfully symbolizes friendship, solidarity, partnership, or a close bond between two women, radiating connection and unity.
